OL,3,CWorld Cup tickets for Iran fans
OL,4,Crevoked, says country's football
OL,5,Cgoverning body
OL,7,FIran's World Cup ticket allocation for
OL,8,Fthe team's group fixtures has been
OL,9,Frevoked, the country's football
OL,10,Fgoverning body has said.
OL,12,FIran is scheduled to play New Zealand
OL,13,Fon June 15 and Belgium on June 21,
OL,14,Fboth at the 70,000-seat Los Angeles
OL,15,FRams' stadium in Los Angeles, before
OL,16,Ffacing Egypt in Seattle on June 26.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
