OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1781075106
OL,3,CWorld Cup tickets for Iran fans
OL,4,Crevoked, says country's football
OL,5,Cgoverning body
OL,7,FUnder FIFA guidelines, each of the 48
OL,8,Fcompeting countries' federations is
OL,9,Fentitled to receive and distribute 8%
OL,10,Fof stadium capacity for each of its
OL,11,Fgames at the World Cup.
OL,13,FJust days before the World Cup opening
OL,14,Fceremony, the Iranian federation
OL,15,Fclaimed in a statement reported by
OL,16,Fsemi-official state media that it was
OL,17,Fnow unable to provide any tickets to
OL,18,Fits supporters.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
