FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1781075106
OL,3,CWorld Cup tickets for Iran fans
OL,4,Crevoked, says country's football
OL,5,Cgoverning body
OL,7,FThe federation claimed the US "once
OL,8,Fagain acted to obstruct the presence
OL,9,Fof Iranian supporters at the stadiums
OL,10,Fhosting the national team's three
OL,11,Fgroup stage matches".
OL,13,FThe Iranian football team has moved
OL,14,Fits squad training base from Tucson,
OL,15,FArizona, to Tijuana, Mexico, after
OL,16,FWashington declined to host the squad
OL,17,Ffor the tournament because of
OL,18,Funcertainty surrounding the current
OL,19,Fwar in the Middle East and wider
OL,20,Fsecurity concerns.
