OL,3,CWorld Cup tickets for Iran fans
OL,4,Crevoked, says country's football
OL,5,Cgoverning body
OL,7,FDespite the ongoing conflict, the US
OL,8,Frejected calls to move the games to
OL,9,Fone of the other host countries.
OL,11,FIran and the US have not had
OL,12,Fdiplomatic ties since the 1980s. Iran
OL,13,Fhas a history of detaining any
OL,14,FAmerican citizen who enters its
OL,15,Fborders, and the US also views harshly
OL,16,Fanyone hoping to enter the US who has
OL,17,Fpreviously visited Iran.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
