OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1781075106
OL,3,CWorld Cup tickets for Iran fans
OL,4,Crevoked, says country's football
OL,5,Cgoverning body
OL,7,FRelations between the two countries
OL,8,Fhave deteriorated further since the
OL,9,Fstart of the US-Israel war with Iran
OL,10,Fthat began on February 28.
OL,12,FThe FFIRI said: "Depriving Iranian
OL,13,Fsupporters of access to their lawful
OL,14,Fand official allocation of tickets is
OL,15,Fan action contrary to the spirit
OL,16,Fgoverning international competitions
OL,17,Fand the principle of equality among
OL,18,Fparticipating countries.
