OL,3,CWorld Cup tickets for Iran fans
OL,4,Crevoked, says country's football
OL,5,Cgoverning body
OL,7,F"This development raises serious
OL,8,Fquestions about the interference of
OL,9,Fnon-sporting and political
OL,10,Fconsiderations in the organisation of
OL,11,Fthe world's biggest football event."
