OL,3,CWorld Cup tickets for Iran fans
OL,4,Crevoked, says country's football
OL,5,Cgoverning body
OL,7,FThe Iranian football team has been
OL,8,Fgiven strict visa conditions, with
OL,9,Fplayers forced to enter and leave US
OL,10,Fterritory on the same day as their
OL,11,Fmatches. The federation has also said
OL,12,Fsome members of backroom staff have
OL,13,Fbeen denied entry into the United
OL,14,FStates.
OL,16,FTrump's administration promised in
OL,17,FJanuary to give athletes and coaches
OL,18,Fvisiting for major sporting events an
OL,19,Fexemption from travel bans, but not
OL,20,Fother officials.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
