OL,3,CWorld Cup tickets for Iran fans
OL,4,Crevoked, says country's football
OL,5,Cgoverning body
OL,7,FIranian citizens were subject to a
OL,8,Ffull travel ban to the US by President
OL,9,FTrump in June last year.
OL,11,FFIFA has been approached for comment.
OL,13,FFrom Westminster to Washington DC -
OL,14,Four political experts are across all
OL,15,Fthe latest key talking points. Listen
OL,16,Fto the latest episode below...
